      "content": "it just feels so pointless though. like i'm just enduring this for the sake of enduring it. there's no \"relief\" coming, no cure, just more of the same. sometimes i look at the idea of just... not being here anymore... and it doesnt even feel scary. it just looks peaceful. like the only way to actually get some rest.",
